<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"ضعيف من قبل حفظه"</span>. <span class="c1">"النتائج"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ٢٥٥)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
